Awp_deathcanyon2 by Sk3tch (www.sk3maps.com)

This map was made from the original for the ESL (http://www.esl.eu/) in thier fun map ladder.  
Differences from the original are as follows:

-Made the map more fair (No longer slightly T sided)
-added more lighting
-Spawn no longer spikes the choke on net_graph 3
-Added slight details to the map (powerlines, etc)

If there are any questions or comments on the map,  email me at sketch76@hotmail.com
